    "description": "在《灰人：人类绑架》中，你将扮演一个男人，他刚刚继承了他哥哥的神秘房子，而他哥哥失踪后，人们认为他已经死了。当你探索你哥哥的家时，你会发现一个隐藏的阁楼，里面堆满了绝密的文件、录音和令人不安的外星人遭遇证据。你越深入这个谜团，你就越能体验到和你哥哥一样的恐惧，奇怪的声音、无法解释的事件，甚至可怕的外星人绑架的可能性。你会发现你哥哥失踪背后的真相吗？还是你会成为未知力量的下一个受害者？<br><br><strong>功能与游戏性 :</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206550/extras/9b27b16e9a5200ff98cd5a513b337369.poster.avif?t=1759327266\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206550/extras/9b27b16e9a5200ff98cd5a513b337369.webm?t=1759327266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206550/extras/9b27b16e9a5200ff98cd5a513b337369.mp4?t=1759327266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>。<br>- 打开抽屉、拿起并检查文件、播放录音，并与灯、门和隐藏隔间互动。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206550/extras/b9ca5c1452a846e58de25648e33e9c9a.poster.avif?t=1759327266\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206550/extras/b9ca5c1452a846e58de25648e33e9c9a.webm?t=1759327266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206550/extras/b9ca5c1452a846e58de25648e33e9c9a.mp4?t=1759327266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> 解锁复杂的谜题。<br>- 解开复杂的谜题，包括寻找钥匙、破译密码和打开神秘的盒子。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206550/extras/ef99bb8f0c4f176f14855962a974ab96.poster.avif?t=1759327266\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206550/extras/ef99bb8f0c4f176f14855962a974ab96.webm?t=1759327266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206550/extras/ef99bb8f0c4f176f14855962a974ab96.mp4?t=1759327266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> 体验可怕的怪声和神秘的盒子。<br>- 体验恐怖的怪声、脚步声、耳语声和阴森恐怖的外星现象。音频设计是游戏的核心组成部分，在您探索和与环境互动的过程中放大了恐惧和害怕。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206550/extras/be2d8448d28b4b8052e9c94b67fac24f.poster.avif?t=1759327266\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206550/extras/be2d8448d28b4b8052e9c94b67fac24f.webm?t=1759327266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206550/extras/be2d8448d28b4b8052e9c94b67fac24f.mp4?t=1759327266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>- 无法解释的事件时有发生，灯光闪烁，阴影在你的眼角移动。当奇怪的事件开始升级时，你需要找到藏身之处。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206550/extras/7d7e93df88a983d3941ac1c00c39cf4f.poster.avif?t=1759327266\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206550/extras/7d7e93df88a983d3941ac1c00c39cf4f.webm?t=1759327266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206550/extras/7d7e93df88a983d3941ac1c00c39cf4f.mp4?t=1759327266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>- 随着故事的深入，恐惧也会不断升级。你发现的越多，危险就越真实<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206550/extras/e7d5b056f512e01a0b3960973c2974b2.poster.avif?t=1759327266\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206550/extras/e7d5b056f512e01a0b3960973c2974b2.webm?t=1759327266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206550/extras/e7d5b056f512e01a0b3960973c2974b2.mp4?t=1759327266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> 游戏有多个结局。<br>- 游戏有多个结局，您在整个游戏过程中的选择将影响结局。",
